32:37.189 --> 32:40.496
are gonna change their ways
and start protecting themselves

32:40.530 --> 32:42.266
against the danger
that you're writing about?

32:42.299 --> 32:44.270
Well, from the sizes
of the crowds

32:44.303 --> 32:46.608
outside the bathhouses
and the bars

32:46.642 --> 32:49.213
and on the street corners,

32:49.246 --> 32:51.417
-I would say "no."
-Hmm.

32:51.450 --> 32:53.421
I think this is a mistake.

32:53.454 --> 32:55.626
There's a predator out there.

32:55.660 --> 32:58.999
Well, how can there not be?

32:59.033 --> 33:03.041
Predators thrive
on decadence and excess.

33:03.074 --> 33:06.314
You know, two doors down
from this very spot,

33:06.347 --> 33:10.322
there is a bar called "The Hole"
where, 24 hours a day,

33:10.355 --> 33:13.127
they employ, as an unpaid
volunteer, a young man

33:13.161 --> 33:14.998
for any and all to enjoy.

33:15.031 --> 33:19.039
Now I enjoy a plump rump
as well as the next man,

33:19.073 --> 33:21.043
but how can the darkness
not feel welcome

33:21.077 --> 33:22.379
in an establishment like that?

33:22.412 --> 33:24.551
I'm not looking for the darkness

33:24.584 --> 33:26.053
as an idea.

33:26.087 --> 33:28.291
I'm looking for... a man.

33:29.326 --> 33:31.130
A man who kills.

33:32.500 --> 33:34.403
I think he's been in this bar.

33:34.436 --> 33:36.140
HENRY:
I've seen him.

33:36.173 --> 33:38.746
Someone like him.

33:38.779 --> 33:41.818
He usually comes in late,
five minutes before closing

33:41.852 --> 33:45.593
when all the unloved queens,
too chubby or too...

33:45.626 --> 33:48.699
sad or too messy
have just about given up hope.

33:48.732 --> 33:52.740
He rides in
to bring the hope back to life.

33:52.774 --> 33:55.045
What does he look like?

33:55.078 --> 33:56.582
(smacks lips)

33:56.615 --> 33:58.752
Honestly,
by the time he comes in,

33:58.786 --> 34:01.758
I'm already too deep
to notice the...

34:01.792 --> 34:03.596
specifics of a man.

34:05.098 --> 34:06.768
Mm.

34:06.802 --> 34:08.772
One thing I can tell you.

34:08.806 --> 34:11.712
He seems drawn to the ones
that like mai tais.

34:12.680 --> 34:15.218
And once he leaves with them,

34:15.252 --> 34:17.289
I never see them again.

34:19.393 --> 34:21.364
Can I use your name
in the article?

34:21.397 --> 34:23.669
So this killer can
come after me next?

34:24.671 --> 34:26.775
I'm in the phonebook,
sweetheart.

34:26.808 --> 34:29.179
No, thank you.

34:30.549 --> 34:32.587
I understand.

34:34.390 --> 34:36.762
-Thanks for your help.
-Mm.

34:48.451 --> 34:50.488
So I have to know
that you're gonna do

34:50.523 --> 34:52.225
whatever it is we ask you to do.

34:52.259 --> 34:54.229
That you're not gonna get there
and back out.

34:54.263 --> 34:55.733
Because our time is
very valuable.

34:58.505 --> 35:00.375
How's your pain threshold?

35:00.408 --> 35:02.379
I came to New York
to be an actor.

35:02.412 --> 35:04.483
I... I wouldn't want
to do anything

35:04.517 --> 35:06.253
