of immense power,

35:16.340 --> 35:19.246
collectors of high art
and beauty

35:19.279 --> 35:20.816
and shock value.

35:22.620 --> 35:25.191
Ruin your reputation?

35:25.225 --> 35:27.797
Baby, I'm offering you
your big break.

35:32.573 --> 35:34.611
(Gino sighs)

35:35.746 --> 35:37.817
(siren wailing)

35:47.302 --> 35:49.473
STRANGER:
You okay, friend?

35:49.507 --> 35:52.580
