what's going on with me.

35:52.613 --> 35:54.951
Looks like maybe someone slipped
something in that drink.

35:54.984 --> 35:56.555
Something's not right.

35:56.588 --> 35:59.561
It's okay. My car's right here.

35:59.594 --> 36:00.930
Don't worry.

36:00.963 --> 36:02.466
You're going to be all right.

36:02.500 --> 36:03.836
Who are you?

36:05.639 --> 36:07.376
(car door closes)

36:16.260 --> 36:18.264
(siren wails in distance)

36:18.297 --> 36:20.335
♪ ♪

36:44.483 --> 36:46.555
FREDDY:
