37:03.756 --> 37:05.893
Nice.

37:05.926 --> 37:08.264
(clicking on table)

37:08.297 --> 37:10.903
And shirt off.

37:10.936 --> 37:14.978
(Sam sniffles loudly, sighs)

37:15.011 --> 37:17.249
Phew. (sniffles)

37:19.319 --> 37:21.357
Mm.

37:22.560 --> 37:24.463
(shutter clicks)

37:24.497 --> 37:25.866
Oh.

37:25.900 --> 37:27.737
Beautiful, Freddy.
Hold that. Right there.

37:27.770 --> 37:29.707
Nice.

37:29.741 --> 37:31.812
Uh, no, wait. What are we...?
Are we shooting for Playgirl?

37:31.845 --> 37:33.916
Or what, huh?

37:33.949 --> 37:36.822
