something worthwhile?

37:40.896 --> 37:42.432
(Sam sniffles)

37:42.466 --> 37:45.305
Get naked, Freddy.

37:45.338 --> 37:48.679
What, you don't want
to be shot by Theo Graves?

37:49.681 --> 37:51.718
Good boy.

37:56.962 --> 37:59.634
I want to see the contact sheets
as soon as you develop.

37:59.667 --> 38:02.305
Some of those are going
into my personal collection.

38:02.339 --> 38:03.675
Hmm.

38:03.709 --> 38:05.311
What? You don't approve?

38:05.345 --> 38:06.815
Worse. I don't care.

38:06.848 --> 38:08.719
(door closes)

38:08.752 --> 38:10.990
Hey, do you remember
that really big leather guy

38:11.023 --> 38:13.595
