38:13.629 --> 38:15.031
Huge guy. Unforgettable.

38:15.064 --> 38:17.035
"Big Daddy" was his name,
I think?

38:17.068 --> 38:19.406
Do you have any idea where he
is, or what his real name was?

38:19.439 --> 38:21.410
I think he's dead.
That's what I heard, anyway.

38:21.443 --> 38:22.747
I want to fuck.
Do you want to fuck?

38:22.780 --> 38:24.316
I got to fuck after that.

38:24.349 --> 38:26.420
Go fuck yourself.

