38:39.413 --> 38:42.352
♪ Ooh, ooh-ooh, ooh ♪

38:42.385 --> 38:47.930
♪ Ooh,
ooh-ooh, ooh ♪

38:51.805 --> 38:53.509
Here you go.

38:53.542 --> 38:55.646
